This product includes software developed for agentic robot grasp and
self-collection workflows.

Third-party components (NOT redistributed in this repository; install
separately and comply with their respective licenses):

- AnyGrasp / GraspNet SDK (proprietary binary + license + weights)
- SAM3 (Meta) — text-prompt segmentation
- Your robot arm ROS stack and camera drivers (reference lab used Agilex Piper
  and Intel RealSense; not required)
- Pinocchio / CasADi (IK backends, via your local arm install)
- Optional external HDF5 episode recorder
